<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="MuTA31">
<l>ivaiyavaṉ kōyi liraṇiyaṉa tāka</l>
<l>mavaicey tariyuruva māṉāṉ – ceviteriyā</l>
<l>nākattā ṉālvētat tuḷḷā ṉaṟavēṟṟāṉ</l>
<l>pākattāṉ pāṟkaṭalu ḷāṉ</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>These are temples of him : the one who became the lion form,</l>
<l>performing a pounding of Hiraṇya’s chest, the one on the snake</l>
<l>that does not perceive with the ears, the one in the four Vedas, the one with</l>
<l>him who receives the [Gaṅgā’s] nectar as part, the one on the milk ocean.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
